{"tid":1253903,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請正視「推文」現象","createTime":"2019-06-23T23:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:32:39.000Z","uid":52477,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a00e34b6a36676ef78e0b58381b6513fd60b5ecd","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:00:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>原文整合轉載</em></strong><br />\n<em>［討論］「推土機」現象：係討論串中應盡量以有營養內容去推貼</em><br />\n<em><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252986\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252986</a><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n運動至今踏入第三個星期，連登多咗好多部人肉推土機。我都受過推土機嘅恩惠，幫忙推起一啲重要嘅「一言堂」貼文（即一樓已是所有資訊，很少討論空間，且急需大眾知道了解）。<br />\n<br />\n依我所見，係因為有大量唔急需討論，或無營養（睇你點判斷）嘅貼文瘋狂引人回文，令到一啲急要上焦點嘅貼文進入「推土機」模式。其實好早已經有，但呢期越來越猖狂，包括我自己都用過。<br />\n<br />\n我只想話，都有好多［討論］串係有大量純推土機係到推，變相令到「回應/對話」之間個樓層距離拉遠咗，爬文同參與討論會有少少吃力，中間會有成堆「推」「Push」「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」等等。我唔係話推土機唔好，大家都係一心機個題目上到熱門一齊討論，但個分寸要適宜。唔知大家又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n另外，見到好多巴打開始做目錄整合同一範疇嘅貼文。呢個絕對係革新嘅嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？係咪應該有啲norms去跟下？「推土機」絕對唔係製造良好討論空間嘅現象。以家有大量議題，例如本星期嘅行動，係未有具體開始討論，只有小貓幾隻（我嘅F5係刷到咁嘅結果，可能你唔係）。<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得大家要面對下呢個現象。以家嘅討論成本同時間成本越來越高，大家都係無意識地硬推自己或人地嘅貼文。呢十幾廿秒其實係無思考咁濟。<br />\n<br />\n一啲有意義嘅post，即沉；行動討論post，即沉；<br />\n分化post，榜首。係咪我地樂見嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n最後，係到多謝之前一部神級推土機 - 紫菜巴，幫手推左兩日G20 Liberation聯署。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎參與討論，以營養回覆作推文。"},{"pid":"81b642427c1963dbef496dc29a59b4030920c56a","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:01:05.000Z","msg":"未有改善前，我只能夠硬推。<br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"7801b06552fa0868f0e3a2d6f024db54a6b8d0cc","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:01:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cbc9a0f03cb97b4eefcb5baf3e5210463cb9b834","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89c801896a5c6f1d7603ca384d479fb33ca3da71","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:02:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d39cd3775a41105215ad2633965bf51cce8754d","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:03:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d3fb37b5b343862a95e9ae23ace87476fb97921","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:03:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df48d8a48682475105f87771e2841f9eb2e379f8","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T23:08:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"51bdf0521c631583f34cc04628b8d8d32d697a35","tid":1253903,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"係 搞到有時睇完1樓就上一頁"},{"pid":"6ad250167d0a0ed1e5e7672441b6a9bd8f8a4ab7","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">@連尼住</span>"},{"pid":"daf37032016cc63360510e82f61ae4a46b552bab","tid":1253903,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"做緊fyp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26f5809775c84f8269a6b51206cb9a6dd47d3df","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf37032016cc63360510e82f61ae4a46b552bab","tid":1253903,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"做緊fyp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"邊個唔係呀呢個時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d118d00bc2dc5da75fe2dabe06e22330828294e9","tid":1253903,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:13:52.000Z","msg":"你幾好嗎 <span style=\"color: gold;\">@連尼住</span>"},{"pid":"a4f8a9ca9e90ad74c86e9b7432382ea9ff112057","tid":12539